{"lemma":"عَجٌّ","slug":"عَجٌّ","root":"ع.ج.ج","root_slug":"ع-ج-ج","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ج-ج","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n28079"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8E%D8%AC%D9%8C%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be noisy, to shout, to exclaim, to pray loudly"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be overcrowded"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be dusty"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ʕad͡ʒ.d͡ʒa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n28079","headword_ar":"عَجَّ","root":"Ej","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, Mgh, O, &c.,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, Msb, K,) or"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (so in the O; [but this is at variance with a general rule;]) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaj~a","text_ar":"عَجَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"with kesr to the medial radical [in the first and second persons,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eajijotu","text_ar":"عَجِجْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eajijota","text_ar":"عَجِجْتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (TA,) aor,"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaj~N","text_ar":"عَجٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EajiyjN","text_ar":"عَجِيجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, A, Mgh, O, Msb, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He cried out,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vociferated;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Daj~a","text_ar":"ضَجَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; accord. to Az,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"supplicating,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"begging aid,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"succour;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) and (K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he raised his voice;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, O, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EajoEaja","text_ar":"عَجْعَجَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) or this signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he cried out, vociferated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"raised his voice, repeatedly;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, TA;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaj~a","text_ar":"عَجَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he raised his voice with the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"talobiyap","text_ar":"تَلْبِيَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"saying"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lab~ayoka","text_ar":"لَبَّيْكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: it is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afoDalu AlHaj~i AlEaj~u AlEaj~u waAlv~aj~u","text_ar":"اَفْضَلُ الحَجِّ العَجُّ العَجُّ وَالثَّجُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, O, Msb) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The most excellent of the actions of the pilgrimage are"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the raising of the voice with the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tlbyp","text_ar":"تلبية"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, O, and Msb in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vj","text_ar":"ثج"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the shedding of the blood of the victims brought for sacrifice to the sacred territory:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, and Msb in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vj","text_ar":"ثج"},{"kind":"text","text":":) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EajiyjN","text_ar":"عَجِيجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"crying out,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vociferating, and clamouring,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a people, or party. (TA.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaj~a","text_ar":"عَجَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. ns. as above, said of a camel,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made a"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"loud"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"noise"},{"kind":"text","text":"in his braying: and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EajoEaja","text_ar":"عَجْعَجَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he repeated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reiterated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a noise:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaj~a","text_ar":"عَجَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EajiyjN","text_ar":"عَجِيجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of water,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it made a sound;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and so [or as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it made a reiterated sound"},{"kind":"text","text":"] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EajoEaja","text_ar":"عَجْعَجَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": and in the same sense the former verb is used in relation to a bow: and also in relation to the [piece of stick of wood called]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zanod","text_ar":"زَنْد"},{"kind":"text","text":"on the occasion of its producing fire: (TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EajoEaja","text_ar":"عَجْعَجَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of camel, when beaten, or heavily laden,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he uttered a grumbling cry;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ragaA","text_ar":"رَغَا"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O, K.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaj~ati Alr~iyHu","text_ar":"عَجَّتِ الرِّيحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AEj~t","text_ar":"اعجّت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The wind was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, violent, and raised the dust,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and drove it along."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [See also 2.] ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaj~ati Alr~aAy^iHapu","text_ar":"عَجَّتِ الرَّايِحَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The odour diffused itself strongly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"powerfully"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A, TA.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaj~a vadoyuhaA","text_ar":"عَجَّ ثَدْيُهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vadoyaAhaA","text_ar":"ثَدْيَاهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) said of a girl, (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Her breast,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"breasts, began to swell,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"become protuberant."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaj~a Alqawomu","text_ar":"عَجَّ القَوْمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AEj~wA","text_ar":"اعجّوا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"haj~uwA","text_ar":"هَجُّوا"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ahj~wA","text_ar":"اهجّوا"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Daj~uwA","text_ar":"ضَجُّوا"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ADj~wA","text_ar":"اضجّوا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[P], as is said in the “ Nawádir, ” (TA,) mean"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^akovaruwA fiY funuwnihimu Alr~ukuwba","text_ar":"اَكْثَرُوا فِى فُنُونِهِمُ الرُّكُوبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) in one copy"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fY funuwnihi","text_ar":"فى فُنُونِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) [Ibr. D thinks that both of these readings are mistranscribed, for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^akovaruwA mino funuwni Alr~ukuwbi","text_ar":"اَكْثَرُوا مِنْ فُنُونِ الرُّكُوبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party, practised many modes,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manners, of riding;"},{"kind":"text","text":"agreeably with an explanation in the TK: but the case is very perplexing; and is rendered the more so by the facts that this is not in the O, and that what here follows is not in the K nor in the TA, and that I do not find in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hj","text_ar":"هج"},{"kind":"text","text":"nor in any other art. anything that throws light upon it:]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaj~a Alqawomu fiY AlwaAdiY","text_ar":"عَجَّ القَوْمُ فِى الوَادِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AEj~wA","text_ar":"اعجّوا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"haj~uwA","text_ar":"هَجُّوا"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ahj~wA","text_ar":"اهجّوا"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaj~uwA","text_ar":"خَجُّوا"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Axj~wA","text_ar":"اخجّوا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[?], mean"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party, descended into the valley, and trod it much."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaj~a Aln~aAqapa","text_ar":"عَجَّ النَّاقَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see R. Q. 1."}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","Msb","K","TA","O","A"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}